channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] NeuralSeek (neuralseek) has a new plan named neuralseek-bring-your-own-llm
item.description: Leverage all of NeuralSeek's features, but instead of using our black-box LLM you connect via our no-code connectors to leading commercial and open-source LLM's. This enables you to run within a single datacenter or country, or choose the commercial LLM that best fits your business and pricing needs.
